Name:                   cab
Version:                0.0.0
Author:                 Kazu Yamamoto <kazu@iij.ad.jp>
Maintainer:             Kazu Yamamoto <kazu@iij.ad.jp>
License:                BSD3
License-File:           LICENSE
Synopsis:               A maintenance command of Haskell cabal packages
Description:            A wrapper to ghc-pkg, cabal, and so on
Category:               System
Cabal-Version:          >= 1.6
Build-Type:             Simple
Executable cab
  Main-Is:              Main.hs
  if impl(ghc >= 6.12)
    GHC-Options:        -Wall -fno-warn-unused-do-bind
  else
    GHC-Options:        -Wall
  Build-Depends:        base >= 4.0 && < 5, process,
                        attoparsec, attoparsec-enumerator,
                        enumerator, bytestring
  Other-Modules:	Commands
                        Help
                        Options
                        Outdated
                        Program
Source-Repository head
  Type:                 git
  Location:             git://github.com/kazu-yamamoto/cab.git
